 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Systems Integration Engineer Prodapt SA United States Job details Job Type Full-time Temporary Full Job Description Roles and Responsibilities 
 To partner with in-house teams and third-party software vendors and contractors to provide technical direction and architecture to design. 
To analyze the functional and non-functional business requirements of IT Demands to produce system designs that are scalable, reliable, reproducible automated deployments, adopt highly compatible and standardized interfaces. 
To prepare high- and low-level design documents for security and further technical review 
Create project and system architecture standards, reference architecture models, deliverables, and best practices 
Assess new computing technologies and relevant industry directions to determine potential value for the enterprise 
Collaborate with various technical teams to develop, expand, and refine comprehensive architecture models that drive enterprise solutions while minimizing siloed solutions 
 Work with the business stakeholders to conduct technical assessments of current state and provide input to the roadmap for future state for enterprise applications and tools 
 Manage and maintain common infrastructure that support systems integration such as Apache, Citrix load balancers and message brokers (queues) 
